				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The PPU fetches the tile data <strong>as it renders</strong> - if you want a particular graphics bank to be used for a specific section of the screen, then you must swap it in (and out) mid-screen, using sprite 0 hit or IRQ timers (or a cycle-timed wait) to determine exactly when to do the switch.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
